#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Download Khan Academy
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Software Requeriments:
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - python 3.x
    - get_flash_video 1.24
    - Linux shell



#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Using
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1 - ) Open the file index and delete the unwanted courses. All courses left in the file will be downloaded.

2 - ) Execute downloadkhanacademy.py giving the following command on the shell
    ./downloadkhanacademy.py

3 - ) The program will open the file index and download the courses in there.


If one or more videos fail to download the script will retry to get them.

You can copy the file indexFULL to index so you can have all courses to choose.

